rts. To us thats incredibly exciting.\r\n\r\nNext up, make sure to check out:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage Leads (Post TBA)</li>\r\n	<li>Manage Contacts (Post TBA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHappy reading!\r\n\r\n</section>','Drop #7: Minimalistic cards design','','publish','open','open','','drop-7-minimalistic-cards-design','','','2014-12-19 18:34:12','2014-12-19 18:34:12','',0,'http://blog.iogrow.com/?p=37',0,'post','',0),(38,1,'2014-12-15 20:13:05','2014-12-15 20:13:05','<h1 class=\"post-title\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://iogrowblog.azurewebsites.net/content/images/2014/Aug/Screen_Shot_2014_08_31_at_11_07_13.png\" alt=\"\" /></h1>\r\n<section class=\"post-content\">Cards are quickly becoming one the best user interfaces design pattern for both desktop and mobile devices.\r\nWe at ioGrow are adopting cards design, away from pages, towards a completely personalised experience built on an aggregation of many individual pieces of content.\r\n\r\nCards are perfect for mobile devices and varying screen sizes. Remember, mobile devices are the heart and soul of the future of your business, no matter who you are and what you do. On mobile devices, cards can be stacked vertically, like an activity stream on a phone.\r\n\r\nWe think there is no getting away from it. Cards are the next big thing in design and the creative arts. To us thats incredibly exciting.\r\n\r\nNext up, make sure to check out:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage Leads (Post TBA)</li>\r\n	<li>Manage Contacts (Post TBA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHappy reading!\r\n\r\n</section>','Drop #7: Minimalistic cards design','','inherit','open','open','','37-revision-v1','','','2014-12-15 20:13:05','2014-12-15 20:13:05','',37,'http://blog.iogrow.com/37-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(39,1,'2014-12-15 20:24:53','2014-12-15 20:24:53','<h1 class=\"post-title\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://iogrowblog.azurewebsites.net/content/images/2014/Aug/Screen_Shot_2014_08_31_at_11_16_45.png\" alt=\"\" /></h1>\r\n<section class=\"post-content\">io Grow has unique tagging and filtering features, with a drag and drop experience. It happens a lot when you need to search for a group of customers using tags other than their companies or names.You can set custom tags and assign them by drag and drop over your company, accounts or even a contact.\r\n\r\nIn addition, you can sort search returns alphabetically, by last added, by last activity or by date added.\r\n\r\nFiltering contacts, accounts, and leads helps you focus your efforts on a specific group of customers and grow the productivity of your business, so if you have hundreds of contacts, leads or accounts Quick Filtering is there for you to get you the information you need instantly.\r\n\r\nNext up, make sure to check:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage Contacts (Post TBA)</li>\r\n	<li>Manage Tasks (Post TBA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</section>','Drop #8: Tags & Quick filtering','','publish','open','open','','drop-8-tags-quick-filtering','','','2014-12-15 20:25:36','2014-12-15 20:25:36','',0,'http://blog.iogrow.com/?p=39',0,'post','',0),(40,1,'2014-12-15 20:24:53','2014-12-15 20:24:53','<h1 class=\"post-title\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://iogrowblog.azurewebsites.net/content/images/2014/Aug/Screen_Shot_2014_08_31_at_11_16_45.png\" alt=\"\" /></h1>\r\n<section class=\"post-content\">io Grow has unique tagging and filtering features, with a drag and drop experience. It happens a lot when you need to search for a group of customers using tags other than their companies or names.\r\n\r\nYou can set custom tags and assign them by drag and drop over your company, accounts or even a contact.\r\n\r\nIn addition, you can sort search returns alphabetically, by last added, by last activity or by date added.\r\n\r\nFiltering contacts, accounts, and leads helps you focus your efforts on a specific group of customers and grow the productivity of your business, so if you have hundreds of contacts, leads or accounts Quick Filtering is there for you to get you the information you need instantly.\r\n\r\nNext up, make sure to check:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage Contacts (Post TBA)</li>\r\n	<li>Manage Tasks (Post TBA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</section>','Drop #8: Tags & Quick filtering','','inherit','open','open','','39-revision-v1','','','2014-12-15 20:24:53','2014-12-15 20:24:53','',39,'http://blog.iogrow.com/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(41,1,'2014-12-15 20:25:36','2014-12-15 20:25:36','<h1 class=\"post-title\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://iogrowblog.azurewebsites.net/content/images/2014/Aug/Screen_Shot_2014_08_31_at_11_16_45.png\" alt=\"\" /></h1>\r\n<section class=\"post-content\">io Grow has unique tagging and filtering features, with a drag and drop experience. It happens a lot when you need to search for a group of customers using tags other than their companies or names.You can set custom tags and assign them by drag and drop over your company, accounts or even a contact.\r\n\r\nIn addition, you can sort search returns alphabetically, by last added, by last activity or by date added.\r\n\r\nFiltering contacts, accounts, and leads helps you focus your efforts on a specific group of customers and grow the productivity of your business, so if you have hundreds of contacts, leads or accounts Quick Filtering is there for you to get you the information you need instantly.\r\n\r\nNext up, make sure to check:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage Contacts (Post TBA)</li>\r\n	<li>Manage Tasks (Post TBA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</section>','Drop #8: Tags & Quick filtering','','inherit','open','open','','39-revision-v1','','','2014-12-15 20:25:36','2014-12-15 20:25:36','',39,'http://blog.iogrow.com/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(42,1,'2014-12-15 20:44:27','2014-12-15 20:44:27','<h1 class=\"post-title\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44\" src=\"http://blog.iogrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/minimal-desktop-wallpaper-simple-is-beautiful.png\" alt=\"minimal-desktop-wallpaper-simple-is-beautiful\" width=\"1299\" height=\"242\" /></h1>\r\n<section class=\"post-content\">The toast of CRM has always been its ability to integrate everything known about or discussed with a given customer so that whoever was interacting with him knew exactly what the history of previous conversations was and could more adroitly address his needs. Unfortunately staff members often have trouble in how to use the CRM correctly to both log and retrieve data, this is why ioGrow focuses on usability and simplicity.</section><section class=\"post-content\">We have cut the clutter out to provide a clean, fast, easy to use CRM without unnecessary features and complexities. Thus ioGrow is designed with simple, intuitive, powerful features to allow maximum efficiency while you are amused, enjoying nice and smooth.Organize all of your companys contacts, opportunities, leads, tasks and share them with the appropriate teams without redundancy and confusion.</section>\r\n<blockquote>\"You dont need a CRM that fights you; you need a CRM that just works!\"</blockquote>\r\nSimplicity is a lost feature in most available CRM platforms; meanwhile it is the Strength point of ioGrow. Stop wasting time struggling with spreadsheets or spam emails, or even using a confusing CRM software, and focus on growing your business. Using ioGrow can significantly boost your teams sales productivity and give you the basic core features and sales tools you just need to grow your business.\r\n\r\nImagine having the ability to view client history, edit accounts, reply to emails, interact with clients, and convert leads and lots more. In a silk , simple interfaces that shows you neatly the data you collect about your customers, so you will be able to target certain needs and products for them more strategically, meaning a platform like this will definitely save you time and increase your sales productivity.','Drop #9: As Simple as your Inbox','','publish','open','open','','drop-9-as-simple-as-your-inbox','','','2014-12-15 20:51:42','2014-12-15 20:51:42','',0,'http: