w can significantly boost your teams sales productivity and give you the basic core features and sales tools you just need to grow your business.\r\n\r\nImagine having the ability to view client history, edit accounts, reply to emails, interact with clients, and convert leads and lots more. In a silk , simple interfaces that shows you neatly the data you collect about your customers, so you will be able to target certain needs and products for them more strategically, meaning a platform like this will definitely save you time and increase your sales productivity.\r\n\r\n</section>','Drop #9: As Simple as your Inbox','','inherit','open','open','','42-revision-v1','','','2014-12-15 20:44:27','2014-12-15 20:44:27','',42,'http://blog.iogrow.com/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(46,1,'2014-12-15 20:51:20','2014-12-15 20:51:20','<h1 class=\"post-title\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44\" src=\"http://blog.iogrow.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/minimal-desktop-wallpaper-simple-is-beautiful.png\" alt=\"minimal-desktop-wallpaper-simple-is-beautiful\" width=\"1299\" height=\"242\" /></h1>\r\n<p class=\"post-title\"></p>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"post-content\">We have cut the clutter out to provide a clean, fast, easy to use CRM without unnecessary features and complexities. Thus ioGrow is designed with simple, intuitive, powerful features to allow maximum efficiency while you are amused, enjoying nice and smooth.Organize all of your companys contacts, opportunities, leads, tasks and share them with the appropriate teams without redundancy and confusion.\r\n<blockquote>\"You dont need a CRM that fights you; you need a CRM that just works!\"</blockquote>\r\nSimplicity is a lost feature in most available CRM platforms; meanwhile it is the Strength point of ioGrow. Stop wasting time struggling with spreadsheets or spam emails, or even using a confusing CRM software, and focus on growing your business. Using ioGrow can significantly boost your teams sales productivi